  "_scope": "VERIFY-SIDE PARITY ONLY. Our verifier MUST accept Scala-produced signatures bit-for-bit. This is the consensus-relevant property: a Scala-signed transaction must verify under our node. Prove-side byte parity (audit's original ask) requires Scala test-harness instrumentation with deterministic RNG and is DEFERRED — see README.md.",
